\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Optimal objective versus timing budget for the fixed-profile wire-aware model. Tighter timing constraints increase the objective across all tested wire profiles, and the back-loaded profile is generally the most expensive.}}{15}{}\protected@file@percent }
